title: Windows XP Pro SP2 English, Gold reloaded version - Activation o
description:
The most important differnce between the origial version and this &quot;Gold Reloaded version&quot; is that the Windows File protection has been disabled; the annoying Windows file protection error message has been disabled.

The installation will not require activation and registration!

Also a number of other improvement are implemented.
Read more about it on the back cover, aslo included as jpg file on this CD.

The product key is included in a file in the root directory.
